ields\nfrom the outer parts of the disk, and also consider two alternative\nexplanations for the multiwavelength emission: hot inner accretion flows and\nirradiation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Oct 2013 09:57:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-17"}
