mal coordinate. A crucial part of our proof is to establish that\nthe Euclidean ground state satisfies the necessary analogs of analyticity and\nreflection positivity with respect to this coordinate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Oct 2013 13:19:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Sep 2014 15:09:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 29 Jan 2015 19:41:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-24"}
